{"tid":260681,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"俞定延集中討論區 (3) 唔是定廷是定延呀oppaya","createTime":"2017-05-27T19:42:45.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-16T18:11:35.000Z","uid":7903,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"c932544cb0d6d30a4dc4b967404ea26f11e583ed","tid":260681,"uid":7903,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-27T19:42:45.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">歡迎來到俞定延集中討論區</span></strong></div><br />\n<br />\n俞定延（韓語：유정연／俞定延 Yoo Jeong Yeon；英語：Yoo Jeong Yeon；1996年11月1日－）是一名韓國的女歌手，女子組合TWICE九名成員之一，也是Girl Crush的代表。 偏左手的雙撇子，是家中三個女兒中的老么，大姊為Yuko Company公司的藝人及前SM Entertainment 練習生孔升妍。隊中擔任第三主唱及副領舞。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/3yc76xA.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2F3yc76xA.jpg&h=eccee68f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://pbs.twimg.com/media/C-6RiHxWsAEsGQl.jpg:large\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpbs.twimg.com%2Fmedia%2FC-6RiHxWsAEsGQl.jpg%3Alarge&h=d1604f9c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n原名：유경완 現已把本名改成유정연<br />\n擔當：Vocal，Model擔當<br />\n出生年月日：1996.11.01<br />\n出生地：韓國京畿道安養市<br />\n血型：O型<br />\n家庭成員：爸爸、媽媽、兩個姐姐(其一為演員孔昇延)<br />\n興趣：玩樂高、看吃美食節目、自毀形象<br />\n特長：模仿成員們<br />\n習慣：翹二郎腿<br />\n暱稱：鴕鳥，無趣哥哥，oppa(請不要當面叫定延這暱稱)，溝女王，大喊包<br />\n座右銘：人生就是選擇!<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=vRd-fTpkqw0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DvRd-fTpkqw0&d=LDk7oFq4p5IGC5z%2Fe%2B73Qv1gJfeR7%2BEkjjir5NquRfg%3D&h=25df0c7a\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=vRd-fTpkqw0</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=l9iMZKanCsA\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3Dl9iMZKanCsA&d=LDk7oFq4p5IGC5z%2Fe%2B73Qv1gJfeR7%2BEkjjir5NquRfg%3D&h=050c761a\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=l9iMZKanCsA</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch